sp;; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MBh.</span>&nbsp; &c.; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to act, proceed, behave, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>R.</span>&nbsp; : <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong><span>Caus.</span></strong> <span class='sdata'>-vartayati</span>, to cause to turn or move round or back or to and fro, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MBh.</span>&nbsp;; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Kāv.</span>&nbsp; &c.; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div> (<span>Ā.</span>) to roll or bring near (<span>Subj.</span> <span class='sdata'>-vartayāte</span>), &nbsp;<span class='ls'>RV. v, 37, 3</span>&nbsp;; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to overthrow, upset (a carriage), &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Hariv.</span>&nbsp;; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to invert, put in a reverse order, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Mṛcch. v, 9/10</span>&nbsp; (read <span class='sdata'>-vartya</span> for <span class='sdata'>-vṛtya</span>); <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to change, barter, exchange, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MBh.</span>&nbsp;; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Hariv.</span>&nbsp; &c.; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to renew (an agreement), &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Mn. viii, 154</span>&nbsp; &c.; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to understand or explain wrongly (words &c.), &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MBh.</span>&nbsp;; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Kāv.</span>&nbsp;; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to turn topsy-turvy <span>i.e.</span> search thoroughly, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>R.</span>&nbsp;; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to destroy, annihilate, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>ib.</span>&nbsp;; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div>to straiten, contract, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Car.</span>&nbsp;; <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div> (<span>Ā.</span>) to cause one's self to be turned round (in having one's head shaved all round), &nbsp;<span class='ls'>TBr.</span>&nbsp;; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>ŚBr.</span>&nbsp; (<span>cf.</span